token.

Any.description:
`Any` contains an arbitrary serialized message along with a
URL that describes the type of the serialized message

@type.description: A URL/resource name that uniquely identifies the type of the serialized message.

adcVirtualWarehouse.title: ADC Virtual Warehouse to set as default for user

v1AdcVirtualWarehouse.title:
An AdcVirtualWarehouse is an Aladdin compatible representation
of a Virtual warehouse found on Snowflake

id.description: id describes the Virtual warehouse name.

name.description: name describes the Virtual warehouse name.

size.description: size describes the Virtual warehouse size.

type.title:
type describes the Virtual warehouse type.
(-- api-linter: aladdin::9027::dictionary-conflicting-types-existing=disabled
 aip.dev/not-precedent: We need to do this because this field actually represents a warehouse from the defined types. --)

autoSuspend.description:
auto_suspend describes the maximum idle time
before the warehouse will be automatically suspended.

autoResume.description:
auto_resume describes if the Virtual warehouse
will be resumed automatically or not.

minClusterCount.description:
min_cluster_count describes the number of
minimum active clusters that will be turned ON.

maxClusterCount.description:
max_cluster_count describes the number of
maximum active clusters that will be turned ON.

scalingPolicy.description:
scaling_policy describes the policy used to
automatically start up and shut down clusters.

initiallySuspended.description:
initially_suspended describes if the Virtual warehouse
will be suspended on creation and only first turned ON while
being used.

comment.description: comment describes any comments associate to the Virtual warehouse.

v1AdcVirtualWarehouseOperationResponse.title: Response payload for methods performing specific operations on AdcVirtualWarehouses, such as suspend or resume warehouse

operationSuccessful.description: Describes the status of operation requested. Value of 'true' denotes successful completion.

operationComment.title: Comment on the status of the operation requested

v1AdcVirtualWarehouseSize.description:
- ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_UNSPECIFIED: UNSPECIFIED
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_XSMALL: XSMALL
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_SMALL: SMALL
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_MEDIUM: MEDIUM
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_LARGE: LARGE
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_XLARGE: XLARGE
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_XXLARGE: XXLARGE
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_XXXLARGE: XXXLARGE
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_X4LARGE: X4LARGE
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_X5LARGE: X5LARGE
 - ADC_VIRTUAL_WAREHOUSE_SIZE_X6LARGE: X6LARGE
v1AdcVirtualWarehouseSize.title: Adc Virtual Warehouse Size
